  "instructions": [
    "preheat oven to 400f (200c).",
    "in a large bowl, mix together fromage frais, onion, garlic, thyme, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "add olive oil and lemon juice to the bowl and mix until well combined.",
    "transfer the mixture to a ceramic dish and arrange on a slate tile.",
    "bake for 20 minutes, then char under broiler for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "remove from oven and let cool for 5 minutes before serving."
